ive-projects.md** — Added CodeCause as new priority project, cleaned up language.\n- **memory/arxiv-daily.md** — Added 2026-03-22 entries (NavTrust, OS-Themis papers).\n- **memory/heartbeat-state.json** — Expanded with background agent schedule and active projects tracking.\n\n**No new untagged TODOs found** in workspace code.\n\n**Still outstanding (manual fixes needed):**\n- 7 Python files with `excessive_print` (test_tracer.py: 20, vllm_latency_profiler.py: 24, upload_and_run.py: 23, etc.)\n- 6 Python files with `long_lines` (moltbook_post.py: 6, verify_post.py: 4, post_reply.py: 1 at 1243 chars!)\n- `memory/improvement_report.json` updated to latest scan\n\n**Manual attention needed:** post_reply.py line 14 is 1243 characters — that's a massive URL string that should be broken up. The print-heavy scripts (test_tracer, vllm_latency_profiler, upload_and_run) have 20+ print calls each and could use logger refactoring when you have a free cycle."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9892,"output":683,"cacheRead":11019,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774224107699}}
